OL,3,CCriminal barristers vote to end legal
OL,4,Caid strike
OL,6,FCriminal barristers in Northern
OL,7,FIreland have voted to end their legal
OL,8,Faid strike after almost 6 months,
OL,9,Fafter coming to an agreement on their
OL,10,Ffees.
OL,12,FA 65% majority of Criminal Bar
OL,13,FAssociation members backed a return to
OL,14,Fall Crown Court cases, following
OL,15,Freforms announced by Justice Minister
OL,16,FNaomi Long. But after half-a-year of
OL,17,Fdispute, hundreds of cases have been
OL,18,Fdelayed.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/13
