PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781966866
OL,3,CCriminal barristers vote to end legal
OL,4,Caid strike
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's most senior judge
OL,7,Fhas welcomed the end of long-running
OL,8,Findustrial action by criminal
OL,9,Fbarristers in the region.
OL,11,FThe legal counsel had withdrawn their
OL,12,Fservices in legally aided crown court
OL,13,Fcases amid a dispute with the
OL,14,FDepartment of Justice.
OL,16,FThey escalated their action in January
OL,17,F` increasing the number of cases
OL,18,Fcovered by the boycott ` in a move
OL,19,Fthat has seen many criminal
OL,20,Fproceedings grind to a halt.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
