FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781966866
OL,3,CCriminal barristers vote to end legal
OL,4,Caid strike
OL,6,FBarristers agreed to participate in a
OL,7,Fsmall number of Crown Court cases as
OL,8,Fpart of derogation arrangements,
OL,9,Fincluding that of Stephen McCullagh
OL,10,Fwho was jailed for 31 years earlier
OL,11,Fthis month for the murder of his
OL,12,Fpregnant girlfriend Natalie McNally in
OL,13,FLurgan in 2022.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/13
