OL,3,CCriminal barristers vote to end legal
OL,4,Caid strike
OL,6,FThe Criminal Bar Association (CBA) has
OL,7,Fnow voted to return to all legally
OL,8,Faided crown court cases following
OL,9,FJustice Minister Naomi Long's
OL,10,Fannouncement earlier in June that she
OL,11,Fwould accept all recommendations of an
OL,12,Findependent review of criminal legal
OL,13,Faid, including an uplift in fee rates.
OL,15,FThe CBA said 65% of its members agreed
OL,16,Fto end the withdrawal of services.
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland's Lady Chief Justice
OL,19,FDame Siobhan Keegan welcomed the move.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
