FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781966866
OL,3,CCriminal barristers vote to end legal
OL,4,Caid strike
OL,6,FA statement issued on her behalf said
OL,7,Fshe had implemented recovery plans to
OL,8,Frestore crown court business as an
OL,9,F"immediate and pressing priority".
OL,11,F"A preparatory period will be required
OL,12,Fto undertake essential preliminary
OL,13,Fwork, including arraignments, pleas
OL,14,Fand sentences, and trial scheduling to
OL,15,Fmaximise court capacity," said the
OL,16,Fstatement.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@aO]sD@AOUwD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781966866
OL,3,CCriminal barristers vote to end legal
OL,4,Caid strike
OL,6,F"It is essential that preparatory work
OL,7,Fis constructive in addressing and
OL,8,Fresolving outstanding matters. The
OL,9,FLady Chief Justices encourages active
OL,10,Fand collaborative engagement to narrow
OL,11,Fthe core issues in cases proceeding to
OL,12,Ftrial.
OL,14,F"To support an efficient return to
OL,15,Fbusiness crown court trials will be re-
OL,16,Flisted and prioritised, with those
OL,17,Fready to proceed brought forward at
OL,18,Fthe earliest opportunity.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781966866
OL,3,CCriminal barristers vote to end legal
OL,4,Caid strike
OL,6,F"Particular emphasis will be placed on
OL,7,Fcases involving the most vulnerable
OL,8,Findividuals, while recognising that
OL,9,Fvulnerability is widely experienced
OL,10,Fand that difficult but necessary
OL,11,Fprioritisation decisions must be made
OL,12,Fin order to address the most urgent
OL,13,Fcases first.
OL,15,F"The judiciary will work urgently and
OL,16,Fcollaboratively with justice partners
OL,17,Fand stakeholders to restore crown
OL,18,Fcourt business as quickly and
OL,19,Feffectively as possible.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781966866
OL,3,CCriminal barristers vote to end legal
OL,4,Caid strike
OL,6,F"The adverse impact of delay and
OL,7,Funcertainty upon participants within
OL,8,Fthe criminal justice system is well
OL,9,Festablished.
OL,11,F"The Lady Chief Justice has
OL,12,Fconsistently highlighted the urgent
OL,13,Fneed for additional resources to
OL,14,Fsupport the effective operation of the
OL,15,Fsystem and to mitigate delay. That
OL,16,Fneed is now more acute than at any
OL,17,Fprevious time."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
