FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781966866
OL,3,CCriminal barristers vote to end legal
OL,4,Caid strike
OL,6,FThe CBA said the withdrawal of
OL,7,Fservices had been a "last resort" in
OL,8,Fresponse to a "deepening access to
OL,9,Fjustice crisis" throughout the
OL,10,Fcriminal justice system.
OL,12,FIn a statement, the association said:
OL,13,F"Over the course of the action, and in
OL,14,Fall of its engagement with
OL,15,Fstakeholders and those affected by its
OL,16,Fwithdrawal of services, the CBA
OL,17,Fremained united and steadfast,
OL,18,Frepeatedly stating that it wanted to
OL,19,Furgently find a resolution that would
OL,20,Fenable all barristers to return to
OL,21,Fwork in all crown court cases.
OL,26,@oD@UOUoD@aO]pD@OOUqD@OO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781966866
OL,3,CCriminal barristers vote to end legal
OL,4,Caid strike
OL,6,F"The CBA welcomes the fact that
OL,7,Fsufficient progress has now been made
OL,8,Fto enable full service to resume and
OL,9,Fappreciates all of the effort and
OL,10,Fengagement that has contributed to
OL,11,Fthis outcome.
OL,13,F"The Criminal Bar Association is
OL,14,Fcommitted to working with criminal
OL,15,Fjustice partners to advance those
OL,16,Fcases that had been impacted by the
OL,17,Fwithdrawal of services.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781966866
OL,3,CCriminal barristers vote to end legal
OL,4,Caid strike
OL,6,F"The withdrawal of services brought
OL,7,Finto stark relief the necessity for
OL,8,Fthe criminal legal aid system to be
OL,9,Fadequately funded and preserved as a
OL,10,Fviable and vital support service to
OL,11,Fall those who require access to
OL,12,Fjustice.
OL,14,F"Continued work and ongoing vigilance
OL,15,Fwill still be required to ensure that
OL,16,Fthe criminal legal aid system is
OL,17,Fplaced on a sustainable footing for
OL,18,Fthe longer term.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781966866
OL,3,CCriminal barristers vote to end legal
OL,4,Caid strike
OL,6,F"The CBA is committed to working
OL,7,Fcollaboratively with the Department of
OL,8,FJustice on an ongoing basis towards
OL,9,Fthat aim and to trying to ensure that
OL,10,Fthere is no relapse back to the acute
OL,11,Fcrisis that has been abated by this
OL,12,Fresolution."
OL,14,FA spokesperson for the Department of
OL,15,FJustice (DoJ) said the vote was a
OL,16,F"positive development".
OL,18,F"The Department of Justice notes the
OL,19,Foutcome of the CBA vote, which is a
OL,20,Fpositive development," the DoJ said in
OL,21,Fa statement.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@LO]xD@AOUxD@VO]zD@AOU|D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
