PN,41413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781966866
OL,3,CCriminal barristers vote to end legal
OL,4,Caid strike
OL,6,F"It is hoped this will result in a
OL,7,Ffull return to services by all members
OL,8,Fand the department will monitor the
OL,9,Fsituation closely."
